title: Newroz International Stadium
text: Newroz International Stadium is a <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="Sulaymaniyah">Sulaymaniyah</a>, <a href="Iraq">Iraq</a>, that is currently under construction. Once completed, it will be used mostly for football matches and will host the home matches of <a href="Newroz%20SC">Newroz SC</a>. The stadium will have a capacity of 14,500 spectators.
